@node "Geschichte" "History"
@next "Main"

    V2.3 (11.07.95) Ok. I think now it should really work (removed a
        bug which caused a system crash when closing the window).
    V2.2 (29.05.95) Removed more bugs.
    V2.1 (10.05.95) As reported, CX crashes when opening its window
        (but CX didn't crash on my system what maked the debugging a bit
        complicated). I Hope, I found the bug and removed. You can now
    also open CX on a pubscreen.
    V2.0 (26.04.95) This version
    V1.3 (19.09.94)
    V1.1 (13.09.94)
    V1.0 (06.09.94) First release

@endnode

